{"total":26,"pageSize":12,"pageCount":3,"data":[{"title":"工具不会帮你解决问题，除非……","uid":"c016b765dd1cbe3495c4d1ef2c90d2dd","slug":"tools-cant-be-solution","date":"2022-06-28T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-29T08:19:25.795Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/tools-cant-be-solution.json","cover":"https://s2.loli.net/2022/06/29/RUHKov3qBtalNd5.png","text":"我是一个很容易不知不觉地沉迷工具或技术中去的人。 换言之，「工具」很容易与「玩具」混同，因为他们都具有相似的结构：在「发现问题」和「解决问题」中提供可行的路径。 所有的玩具都解决了孩子们或成年人的一些问题。 孩子们丰富的想象力需要借助实体物品来释放——汽车、乐高、芭比娃娃等等。 ...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.2k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"数字健康","slug":"数字健康","count":4,"path":"api/categories/数字健康.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"工具","slug":"工具","count":1,"path":"api/tags/工具.json"}],"author":{"name":"桌沿","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/me.png","link":"/","description":"桌沿奇思 Newsletter 主理人，少数派签约作者","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"sspai":{"icon":"/svg/sspai.svg","link":"https://sspai.com/u/379wzx2e/posts"},"newsletter":{"icon":"/svg/newsletter.svg","link":"https://deskside.zhubai.love"},"jike":{"icon":"/svg/jike.svg","link":"https://okjk.co/IktPrE"},"mailto":{"icon":"/svg/mailto.svg","link":"mailto:deskside.zhuoyan@outlook.com"}}}},"feature":true},{"title":"坐下来和父母好好聊聊","uid":"3203a53576950b7fac4853e612b33dcf","slug":"sit-and-talk-with-parents","date":"2022-05-20T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-29T08:05:28.402Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/sit-and-talk-with-parents.json","cover":"https://s2.loli.net/2022/06/29/iIQ3KbTXxn5J9PC.png","text":"曾有人说，我们和父母是最熟悉的陌生人。 谁说不是呢？ 有多少人在成年以后，还能和父母（哪怕其中一方）敞开心扉，认真地聊聊自己的理想、价值观、生活态度？甚至是对方让自己感到不舒服的点，我们都几乎很少触及，因为我们害怕家庭里微妙的关系平衡被打破。 因为近期我都在家里住，因此不可避免地...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"论他人作为自己","slug":"论他人作为自己","count":6,"path":"api/categories/论他人作为自己.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"沟通","slug":"沟通","count":2,"path":"a